items.summary: Remove the public-facing footer attribution/link to caffeine (including any caffeine.ai/caffeine.xyz/caffine.xyz URLs and UTM parameters) from the website UI, and replace it with a simple English copyright line for the shop.

Remove or replace any references to the domain "caffeine.xyz" or "caffine.xyz" in repository documentation and configuration examples (e.g., deployment/domain docs), using a neutral placeholder domain (e.g., "example.com") if an example is needed.
